title: Eating Out - Drama Camp
description: There's no shortage of drama or camp in the fourth instalment of Q. Allan Brocka's hilarious Eating Out series. Zack and Casey's relationship is in a slump, but things are about to change at Dick Dickey's Drama Camp. Zack meets gorgeous Benji, and when they get cast as lovers in a sexed-up version of The Taming of the Shrew, their self-restraint is put to the test. Will Zack and Casey's relationship last with Benji in the picture?
